\pageTitle{What is EuRuKo?}
\bigskip
\begin{center}
EuRuKo is an annual non-profit tech conference with an accent on
Ruby and satellite technologies.\linebreak

It is the second largest Ruby community gathering in the world.\linebreak

In 2016 EuRuKo will be in Sofia. We expect around
700 attendees from all around the globe, the majority of
whom are Ruby and JavaScript developers.\linebreak

For more information about EuRuKo: {\color{blue} \url{http://euruko.org/}}
\end{center}
